sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant App as Consuming App
    participant AS as enclaveapp-app-storage<br/>(backend selection)
    participant Core as enclaveapp-core<br/>(traits + metadata)
    participant Cache as enclaveapp-cache<br/>(envelope + counter)
    participant Backend as Platform Backend<br/>(apple/windows/linux-tpm/keyring)
    participant HW as Secure Element<br/>(SE / TPM / FIDO2)
    participant Disk as On-Disk Artifacts

    Note over App,Disk: ENCRYPT FLOW

    App->>AS: store_secret(label, plaintext)
    AS->>Core: validate label + resolve policy
    Core->>Disk: read key metadata (.meta)
    Disk-->>Core: metadata (access policy, backend type)
    Core->>Core: verify metadata HMAC tag

    AS->>Backend: encrypt(plaintext, key_handle)
    Backend->>HW: ECDH key agreement (P-256)
    HW-->>Backend: shared secret (never leaves hardware)
    Backend->>Backend: HKDF-SHA256 → AES-256-GCM key
    Backend->>Backend: AES-256-GCM encrypt

    opt Cache enabled
        Backend->>Cache: wrap with cache envelope
        Cache->>Disk: update rollback counter (monotonic)
    end

    Backend-->>AS: ciphertext + nonce + tag
    AS->>Disk: write ciphertext (.enc)
    AS-->>App: success

    Note over App,Disk: DECRYPT FLOW

    App->>AS: load_secret(label)
    AS->>Core: validate label + resolve policy
    Core->>Disk: read key metadata (.meta)
    Core->>Core: verify metadata HMAC tag

    AS->>Disk: read ciphertext (.enc)
    Disk-->>AS: ciphertext + nonce + tag

    opt Cache enabled
        AS->>Cache: verify cache envelope
        Cache->>Disk: verify rollback counter
        alt Counter mismatch
            Cache-->>AS: Error: rollback detected
            AS-->>App: Error
        end
    end

    AS->>Backend: decrypt(ciphertext, key_handle)
    Backend->>HW: ECDH key agreement (P-256)

    opt User presence required (biometric policy)
        HW->>HW: Touch ID / Hello / PIN prompt
    end

    HW-->>Backend: shared secret
    Backend->>Backend: HKDF-SHA256 → AES-256-GCM key
    Backend->>Backend: AES-256-GCM decrypt + verify tag

    alt Tag verification fails
        Backend-->>AS: Error: tampered ciphertext
        AS-->>App: Error
    else Success
        Backend-->>AS: plaintext
        AS-->>App: plaintext (caller must zeroize when done)
    end
